text: Holly Springs is a city in and county seat of Marshall County, Mississippi, United States at the border with southern Tennessee. It is near the Mississippi Delta. The population was 6,968 at the 2020 census. ==References== ==Other websites== * Holly Springs Ledger, 1837-1904 (MUM00232) at the University of Mississippi.
